納上訴審裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　6 　　月　　29　　日\r\n                              書記官  張莉秋","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/OLEV/110%2c%e5%93%a1%e7%b0%a1%2c93%2c20210629%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"OLEV,110,員簡,93,20210629,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"員簡","JNO":"93","JDATE":"20210629","JTITLE":"清償債務"}